data.description: Welcome to your oasis! This beautiful pool home sits on a triple lot with lush and mature landscaping.  The property has been completely updated providing you with comfort and ease.  As you enter through the screened-in front porch, you will be greeted by the open floor plan, perfect for entertaining guests or relaxing with loved ones.  The open kitchen was remodeled in 2022 with brand-new cabinets, granite countertops, and new appliances.  Enjoy cooking while overlooking the pool area or conversing with your guests in the living room.  From the kitchen, step outside to your covered lanai, overlooking the pool area and spacious fenced-in backyard.  This home offers so much outdoor living and entertaining space.  Enjoy your days by relaxing in the pool, on your lanai, sitting outside on your newly paved outdoor area, gardening in your spacious backyard, or relaxing in your brand-new hot tub while overlooking the green space.  After a relaxing day in the sun, shower in the beautiful primary upgraded shower, remodeled in 2020. This property is conveniently located in SW Cape Coral, close to multiple amenities such as Surfside shops, Cape Coral Sports Complex, Sun Splash waterpark, Gator Mikes, and so much more!  Enjoy eating out at local restaurants such as Bonefish Grill, Carrabba's Italian Grill, etc.      The property also has the following major updates, roof in 2022, pool cage in 2023, pool resurfaced in 2020, privacy fence in 2023, A/C 2023, bamboo flooring in 2021, bathrooms were redone in 2020, exterior paint in 2023, new pool pump motor in 2023, electric pool heater in 2022, brand new pavers and hot tub purchased in 2024, brand a new pressure tank on well for irrigation, and recently added water drain all around outside of the pool.
